How HTML and CSS connect
class="header" is written in HTML
.header in CSS means “style the element whose class is header

So this HTML:
<div class="header">My Website</div>

gets the CSS styling from:
.header{
  background: lightblue;
}
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

In CSS:
.header → selects class="header"
#header → selects id="header"
div → selects all div elements
																																
                                                                  
